name: Jennifer Lopez
description:

Jennifer Lopez: Her interest in becoming famous arose from having a supporting role in the movie My Little Girl. In 1991, she got her first job as a dancer and in 1993 she decided to pursue acting. She got her first leading role in the movie Selena, with which she earned over a million dollars and was also nominated for a Golden Globe as best actress. She also starred in the first installment of the film series Anaconda (1997). The following year, with the movie Out of Sight (1998), she managed to collect two million dollars2 and also gave one of the best performances of her career. In 1999, she debuted as a singer with her single If You Had My Love which was number one on the Billboard Hot 100 and with her album On the 6 (1999), enjoying great success in the international market.
